<plot>Abigail is the story of a spoiled rich girl, the only daughter of a well-known businessman, beautiful and troubled, who falls in love with her literature professor at San Lazaro prep school. And so begins the odyssey of love that juggles an unfortunate marriage, a child, neglectful parents until Abigail and Carlos Alfredo are happily united.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?021283</url></doc>
